'''[[Cusmaan]]''' '''[[Cusmaan binu Caffan]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: ʻUthmān ibn ʻAffān; [[carabi]]: ﻋﺜﻤﺎﻥ ﺑﻦ ﻋﻔﺎﻥ; magaca dhamaystiran Cusmaan ibn Caffan "ﻋﺜﻤﺎﻥ ﺑﻦ ﻋﻔﺎﻥ") dhashay 577 [[C.D]] magaalada Daa'if ee dhulka Carabta, isla markaana dhintey 20 June 656 C.D (18kii Dulhijjah
35 Hijrada ka dib), wuxuu ahaa saaxiibka sadexaad ee [[Nebi Muxamed]], hogaamiyihii afaraad ee [[Islam|dowlada Islaamka]], asxaabi ka mid ah [[Khaliif|Kulafo Raashidiinta]] iyo mid ka mid ah asxaabta rasuulka.<ref>"'''[[Cusmaan bin Caffan]]'''"</ref><ref>"[[ingiriis]]: ʻUthmān ibn ʻAffān; [[carabi]]: ﻋﺜﻤﺎﻥ ﺑﻦ ﻋﻔﺎﻥ; magaca dhamaystiran Cusmaan ibn Caffan "ﻋﺜﻤﺎﻥ ﺑﻦ ﻋﻔﺎﻥ""</ref>'''<ref name=i4u>[http://www.islam4theworld.net/sahabah/abu_bakr_r.htm], from [[islam4theworld]]</ref> 

Cusmaan binu Caffan wuxuu ka dhashay qabiilka [[Ummayad]] ee reer [[Makka]] kuwaasi oo ahaa reer awood badan oo ka tirsan beel-weynta [[Quraysh]]. 
Cusmaan wuxuu ahaa hogaamiye ka mid ah [[Khaliif|khulafo al-Raashidiinta]] kaasi oo talada iyo hogaanka maamulka [[Islaam|dowlada Islaamka]] la wareegay asagoo ah [[sanad|65 jir]], ka dib markii uu [[Cumar bin Khattab]] dhintey.<ref>"hogaamiye sare ee maamulka [[Islaam|dowlada Islaamka]]"</ref> 

Wakhtigii uu hogaanka maamulka dowlada Islaamka hayay Cusmaan wuxuu gaadhsiiyay heer aad u sareeysa isla markaana uu qabsaday dhul aad u badan ooy ka mid yihiin [[Beershiya|boqortooyadii Beershiya]] (dhulka maanta loo yaqaano [[Iiraan]]), meelo ka mid ah Khorasan (deegaanada maanta lagu magacaabo wadanka [[Afghanistan]]) iyo meelo badan oo ka mid ah [[Yurub|bariga Yurub]].<ref name="brit">[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/2153/Abu-Bakr], from [[Encyclopædia Britannica]]</ref> 

Intii [[nebi]]gu noolaa, Cusmaan bin Caffan wuxuu ahaa saaxiibka iyo la-taliyaha sadexaad ee [[Nebi Muxamed]] asagoo kala qeyb galay arimo aad u badan. Wuxuuna ka garab dagaalamay Nebi Muxamed qaswado aad u badan ooy ka mid yihiin [[Dagaalkii Beder]], [[Dagaalkii Uxud]], [[Dagaalkii Dhufeysyada]],<ref>"[[Dagaalkii Beder]], [[Dagaalkii Uxud]], [[Dagaalkii Dhufeysyada]]"</ref> qabsashaddii magaalada [[Makka]], [[Dagaalkii Kheybar]], [[Dagaalkii Xunayn]], go'doomintii Daa'if iyo [[Dagaalkii Tabuk]].<ref>"qabsashaddii magaalada [[Makka]], [[Dagaalkii Kheybar]], [[Dagaalkii Xunayn]], go'doomintii Daa'if iyo [[Dagaalkii Tabuk]]"</ref>
Dagaaladani wuxuu Abu Bakr ku kharash gareeyay in badan oo dhaqaalihiisa ka mid ah. 

Si kastaba ha ahaatee, goortii [[Nebi Muxamed]] geeriyooday waxaa [[Rashidiinta|khulafo Raashidiintu]] si waafaqsan dardaarankii nebiga isla garteen in Abu Bakr lagu wareejiyo hogaanka iyo talada maamulka dowladii Islaamka. Wakhtigani waxaa dhacday khilaaf aad u wayn oo dad badan ayaa [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka dib uga noqdey maadaama nebigii waxyigu ku soo dagayay geeriyooday. 

